CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FA prison officer who formed a
OL,7,Frelationship with a sex offender has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for six months.
OL,10,FLivvy Edney, 44, became involved with
OL,11,Finmate Paul Young while working at HMP
OL,12,FChannings Wood in Devon.
OL,14,FExeter Crown Court heard Edney began
OL,15,Fworking at the prison in 2020 and
OL,16,Fstarted the relationship with Young in
OL,17,FNovember 2022 after becoming his
OL,18,Fsupervisor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FThe prison authorities became
OL,7,Fsuspicious and Young, serving a
OL,8,Fsentence of imprisonment for public
OL,9,Fprotection after being convicted of
OL,10,Fassault by penetration, was
OL,11,Ftransferred to another institution in
OL,12,FJanuary 2023.
OL,14,FEdney used two pay as you go mobile
OL,15,Fphones, registered a false name and
OL,16,Fgave an address of a relative of Young
OL,17,Fto the prison authorities to keep in
OL,18,Ftouch with him after he was moved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FThe court heard their telephones calls
OL,7,Fwere recorded by the prison
OL,8,Fauthorities, in which they declared
OL,9,Ftheir love for each other.
OL,11,FYoung also read out poetry he had
OL,12,Fwritten for Edney, and they discussed
OL,13,Fplans for taking a trip to Venice
OL,14,Fafter he was released.
OL,16,FEdney was arrested at her home in
OL,17,FMarch 2023 and in police interviews
OL,18,Fdenied any relationship with Young or
OL,19,Fknowledge of the two mobile phones
OL,20,Ffound at her address.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FYoung's cell was also searched and
OL,7,Fletters, notes and a Valentine's card
OL,8,Ffrom Edney were recovered.
OL,10,FThe card depicted two penguins and
OL,11,Fcontained a "sexually intimate"
OL,12,Fmessage.
OL,14,FEdney, from Grenville Avenue, in
OL,15,FTorquay, previously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FLee Brembridge, defending, urged the
OL,7,Fcourt to impose a suspended prison
OL,8,Fsentence as the mother of three had
OL,9,Fsince remarried, had a full-time job
OL,10,Fand was unlikely to reoffend.
OL,12,F"She is not the youngest prison
OL,13,Fofficer, but there is a degree of
OL,14,Finexperience in terms of the work that
OL,15,Fshe had performed up to the period of
OL,16,Fher ill health," he said.
OL,18,F"It really should be set against the
OL,19,Fbackground that she is someone who has
OL,20,Fher own vulnerabilities.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@PO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,F"Her vulnerabilities are very personal
OL,7,Fto her, which started in her
OL,8,Fchildhood, and indeed continued in a
OL,9,F20-year relationship with her ex-
OL,10,Fhusband.
OL,12,F"Mrs Edney has spent a lifetime living
OL,13,Fwith anxiety, with depression, and
OL,14,Feverything which comes with a
OL,15,Ftraumatic childhood, which then
OL,16,Ffollows its way into an abusive
OL,17,Fmarriage over the course of 20 years.
OL,19,F"Her life, indeed both her family life
OL,20,Fand her personal life, are now more
OL,21,Fstable than they have ever been."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FJailing Edney for six months, Judge
OL,7,FJames Patrick said she was fully aware
OL,8,Fof the "importance of maintaining
OL,9,Fboundaries in relation to prisoners".
OL,11,F"Paul Young is somebody who had had a
OL,12,Frelationship with another officer in
OL,13,Fthe past and that was something which
OL,14,Fintrigued you," he said.
OL,16,F"From that period, you and he
OL,17,Fdeveloped a relationship which became
OL,18,Fcloser and closer.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@dO]sD@AOUvD@OO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,F"The prison authorities were concerned
OL,7,Fabout you and your closeness with him
OL,8,Fand as a result of which he was
OL,9,Ftransferred to another prison.
OL,11,F"That should have served as a warning
OL,12,Fto you, but it did not. It's clear
OL,13,Fthat you then started to set about
OL,14,Fmaking contact with him.
OL,16,F"You did so using subterfuge, you did
OL,17,Fso by pretending to be somebody else,
OL,18,Fyou did so using disguised telephone
OL,19,Fnumbers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,F"You declared in those calls your love
OL,7,Ffor one another, you read out poems,
OL,8,Fyou discussed dating, you discussed
OL,9,Fmeeting, there were multiple
OL,10,Freferences to sexual behaviour.
OL,12,F"It can be said on your behalf that
OL,13,Fyou brought the contact to an end.
OL,15,F"That said of course you brought the
OL,16,Fcontact to an end, knowing firstly,
OL,17,Fthat he had been transferred, and
OL,18,Fsecondly being very suspicious as to
OL,19,Fwhat the authorities knew about you."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FThe judge added: "I accept that
OL,7,Fthere's no evidence that there was any
OL,8,Fphysical relationship.
OL,10,F"But plainly, your relationship was
OL,11,Fhighly sexual, even if it was not
OL,12,Fphysical.
OL,14,F"In my judgment, and with great
OL,15,Fregret, I conclude that I must send
OL,16,Fyou immediately to custody."
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777057867
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed for relationship
OL,4,Cwith an inmate
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Will Martel, of the
OL,7,FSouth West Regional Organised Crime
OL,8,FUnit, said: "Edney went to significant
OL,9,Flengths to conceal the relationship,
OL,10,Fknowing that it was a serious breach
OL,11,Fof her position.
OL,13,F"Corruption will not be tolerated
OL,14,Fwithin our prisons.
OL,16,F"Working closely with the Prison
OL,17,FService, staff across the prison
OL,18,Festate and wider policing partners, we
OL,19,Fwill continue to root out misconduct
OL,20,Fof this nature."
OL,26,@pD@MOUuD@AOUxD@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
